{"tid":1472162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有人登廣告","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:41:06.000Z","uid":290456,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9f692c76a07f46494f8dc467449b069257b697f8","tid":1472162,"uid":290456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:13:51.000Z","msg":"代po<br />\n<br />\n有個老人家用左6位數<br />\n聽日係蘋果&amp;頭條新聞登廣告<br />\n希望大家祈下禱<br />\nsing hallelujah to the lord咁&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AQnzvXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAQnzvXG.jpg&h=917f248f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 識個老人家，老人家話想知後生仔點睇，會send條link俾佢睇"},{"pid":"8682d609fc007175d40d1441842a86063e56dbc8","tid":1472162,"uid":203734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"個實際用途好似不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff5c4e451deb9e402ac77c591b4d1b34e815e22","tid":1472162,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff803c16a97e224ac5f4f3384ac103b363258ce1","tid":1472162,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼，以牙還牙，以手還手，以腳還腳<br />\n出埃及記21:24<br />\n<br />\n你不要可憐他，要以命償命，以眼還眼，以牙還牙，以手還手，以腳還腳<br />\n申命記19:21<br />\n<br />\n不要以為我來是要給地上帶來和平；我來不是要帶來和平，而是要帶來刀劍。馬太福音10:34<br />\n<br />\n和平之前是先要有公義,公義就是犯罪的被制裁,負出代價<br />\n寛恕不代表人不需負出罪的代價<br />\n没有公義的和平是虛偽可恥,就如1984某d人比其他人更公平"},{"pid":"50f4f5e66fe38913cfc45d31c3ca44710a89625d","tid":1472162,"uid":290456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"多謝你地，老人家真心想知<br />\n<br />\n利申: 佢有捐款去612<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c6ff2ec3801cdb57894f7a744bad62318e5716","tid":1472162,"uid":9096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係用愛係感動唔到啲畜牲"},{"pid":"00450871eba50d05bc90016012cc5237724f2e0e","tid":1472162,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"多謝你無私既付出<br />\n大家宗教信仰未必相同<br />\n亦未敢奢救你既上主會幫忙<br />\n我地會繼續做我地可以做到既事"}]}